videos.headline: Mitchell outleaps his defender for a Miss. State TD
videos.description: Tommy Stevens throws one for the end zone and Osirus Mitchell climbs the ladder and hauls it in for a 33-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mitchell outleaps his defender for a Miss. State TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Hill plunges in for his 2nd TD
videos.description: Kylin Hill falls into the end zone for his second score of the game to increase Mississippi State's lead on Arkansas.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hill plunges in for his 2nd TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Mississippi State increases lead with pick-6
videos.description: Marcus Murphy steps in front of Ben Hicks' pass and goes 32 yards the other way for the Mississippi State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mississippi State increases lead with pick-6) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Gibson dives to the end zone for a score
videos.description: Nick Gibson finds a hole and scampers 47 yards for the Mississippi State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gibson dives to the end zone for a score) 2019/11/02
